org.qcri.rheem.core.types

Class DataSetType<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.qcri.rheem.core.types.DataSetType<T>

  • public class DataSetType<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A data set is an abstraction of the Rheem programming model. Although never directly materialized, a data set keeps track of type and structure of data units being passed between operators.
